

Mixer controls should be exported as Resources (Parameters).




use dbus & hotplug




auto-set mixer elems when finding a new sound device




to record with the mic-in:

    use gnome-alsamixer

    turn up mic gain, turn off mic mute, enable mic record

    turn up capture gain, enable capture record

    arecord -D hw:0,0 -f S16_LE -c 2 test.wav

